{{Quote|On your way out, be sure to try the zwil cakes at the bar. Not addictive unless you're a Drovian.|Leb Slesher, to a spacer|<ref name="SWG:AED">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>}}
'''Zwil''' was a popular flavoring substance, added to cakes on [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Algara II]]. It had a taste of a mixture of [[Vanilla/Legends|vanilla]] and cinnamon. It had a weak narcotic effect on [[Drovian]]s from [[Nim Drovis]] and it was very popular among them. It was ingested through membrane-lined breathing tubes in fist-sized plugs. About eighty-percent of Drovian soldiers were addicted to zwil.

The [[Shistavanen/Legends|Shistavanen]] spicelord [[Volven Roxe]] was also addicted to a variation known as [[Drovian zwil]], though he never traded it himself.

